reviewText: Hey, this movie had great cars that were expensive and awesome. The son of the late Steve McQueen made his movie ever. For a low budget off-screen film it was worth watching it a 1,000 times over. Jan-Michael Vincent, Roxanna Zal, Corey Feldman, Dom DeLouise and Michael Madsen jion the cast of cool and twisted. Gotta Love It!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
